--------------------------------------------------------------------
Third-party components requiring attribution
--------------------------------------------------------------------

This project uses open-source components from the React, TanStack, Vite,
Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui, Radix UI, TipTap, PDF.js, React PDF Viewer,
Highlight.js, Unified, and xlsx ecosystems.

Notable dependencies include:

  - React
  - TanStack Router, Query, Store, Form, Table, Virtual, and Hotkeys
  - Vite and Vite+
  - Tailwind CSS
  - shadcn/ui and Radix UI primitives
  - ofetch
  - WuKongIM JavaScript SDK
  - TipTap and ProseMirror
  - pdfjs-dist and React PDF Viewer
  - react-markdown, remark, rehype, unified, and related plugins
  - highlight.js and react-syntax-highlighter
  - xlsx

A complete dependency inventory is maintained by package manifests and the
lockfile. For redistribution or commercial use, please review each upstream
project's license terms.
